# Meaning of Arrays

---

## right_sum

```python
[15,11,3,0]
```

These are exactly:

```text
right sums
```

for each index.

---

| Index | Right Sum |
| ----- | --------- |
| 0     | 15        |
| 1     | 11        |
| 2     | 3         |
| 3     | 0         |

---

## left_sum

```python
[22,14,10,0]
```

These are left sums but generated in reverse order.

---

| Value | Actual Index |
| ----- | ------------ |
| 22    | index 3      |
| 14    | index 2      |
| 10    | index 1      |
| 0     | index 0      |

---

